      <akn:section eId="sec_31_3931_11">
        <akn:num>31-3931.11</akn:num>
        <akn:heading>Requirements for transacting business.</akn:heading>
<akn:subsection eId="subsec_31-3931_11_a">
      <akn:num>(a)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>A captive insurer shall not transact business in the District unless the captive insurer and, if applicable, each protected cell of a captive insurer, first obtains a certificate of authority from the Commissioner.</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection><akn:subsection eId="subsec_31-3931_11_b">
      <akn:num>(b)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>In determining whether to grant the approval required in subsection (a) of this section, the Commissioner shall consider:</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection><akn:subsection eId="subsec_31-3931_11_c">
      <akn:num>(c)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>A captive insurer shall:</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection><akn:subsection eId="subsec_31-3931_11_d">
      <akn:num>(d)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>The board of directors of a captive insurer shall meet at least one time each year in the District.</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection><akn:subsection eId="subsec_31-3931_11_e">
      <akn:num>(e)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>Repealed.</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection><akn:subsection eId="subsec_31-3931_11_f">
      <akn:num>(f)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>Notwithstanding subsection (a) of this section, a captive insurer that obtains a provisional certificate of authority may engage in limited activities as part of the initial organization and capitalization of the captive insurer.</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection>
      </akn:section>
